<p>Monday 25/6/17<br/>Night march and assault, returned at 6.30 am, went to Bde in afternoon, saw Bas.<br/>Tuesday 26/6/17<br/>Wrote to Doff. Training as usual saw Bas again.<br/>Wednesday 27/6/17<br/>Most lovely photo of Doff received, very good indeed.<br/>Thursday 28/6/17<br/>Field Firing in morning, raining in afternoon.<br/>Friday 29/6/17<br/>Battalion Scheme &amp; inspection in afternoon.<br/>Saturday 30/6/17<br/>Raining heavily in afternoon, had a game of Cards.</p>
